Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十七\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thirty seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.03,0:03:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}立即杀死马库斯・查普林
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪儿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我派琼斯去找你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I sent Jones to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want to talk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.99,0:04:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  山姆  我知道你现在的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, Sam, I know what you're going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也经历过  我知道...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been there. I know that--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艇长  请别...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, please....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道找到正确的途径释放悲伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know that finding the right way to grieve
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很难的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is never easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不必一个人硬抗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you do not have to do this alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当年你也在我身边陪着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}God knows you were there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府派了一艘驱逐舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The administration has sent a destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拦截中国的供给船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to intercept the Chinese supply ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.29,0:04:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要指挥科罗拉多号进行干预作战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm taking the "Colorado" out to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵们正在挨饿  大家都撑不住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our people are starving. Everyone's falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要那艘船上的供给品\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need the food and supplies on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在干什么  艇长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we doing here, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在干什么  我以为我们是要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are we doing? I thought we were supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揭发真相  然后回家去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}getting to the truth so we could all get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不才是我们该干的事情吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Isn't that what we're supposed to be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得先活下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to survive first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么活  和中国结盟吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How, by aligning with the Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.89,0:04:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么能让我们回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How does that get us home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得还有别的选择吗  副艇长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see any other options, X.O.?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在处在孤立无援的状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's not a whole bunch of folks stepping up to take our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候我们也开始卑躬屈膝了  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't realize we had our hat in hand, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是绝对不会让岛民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I will not allow the people of this island 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.46,0:05:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和士兵们挨饿的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and our people to starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不参与这件事  我妻子也不会死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't do this, my wife didn't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去做你的三流香蕉国国王吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so you could become king of some third-rate Banana Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被革职了  指挥官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're relieved, commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早决定走了  艇长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm way ahead of you, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都疯了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Have you all lost your minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在美利坚合众国策划一场政变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A coup d'etat in the United States of America,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.80,0:05:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说得是这个意思吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that is what you're talking about, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议长先生  如果我们不采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Speaker, if we don't act,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上就不会再有美利坚合众国了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there won't be a United States of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第188号行政令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Executive Order 188,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由总统亲自签发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}issued by the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令一队海豹突击队员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}directing a team of Navy SEALs
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗杀奥斯卡・尼尔斯博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to assassinate Dr. Oscar Nils,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联合国派遣到巴基斯坦的武器核查员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the U.N. Weapons inspector in Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.46,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核实了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This has been verified?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份命令是真实有效的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is an authentic order, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.78,0:05:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说  确定命令被执行了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, has it been verified that the order was carried out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.53,0:05:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监察员已经死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The inspector is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴基斯坦人干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the hands of the Pakistanis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  康尼  是我们干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, Connie. We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们杀了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的海豹突击队员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our SEALs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.13,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上将  你应该在牢里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're supposed to be in jail, admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外人的眼里  我是在牢里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as anyone knows, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.69,0:06:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是有几个小人物朋友的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just have a few friends in low places.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.61,0:06:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我们得马上离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. We all need to walk outta here this very second,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以免谁说了什么不可挽回的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}before somebody says something they're gonna regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议长先生  你知道我通常不介意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Speaker, you know I'm not generally squeamish
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以武力先下手为强\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}about the preemptive use of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本人也曾亲自\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In fact, I've personally jammed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止了你几项拨款法案的通过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}quite a few appropriation bills past you in my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政治上来说  我可以说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And since politically, I straddle a line
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}匈奴帝国领袖  凶残野蛮  被认为是文明社会的公敌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比匈奴王阿提拉强不了多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}just slightly to the left of Attila the Hun,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you will believe me when I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.55,0:06:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我参与这件事不是为了搞垮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did not get into this in order to take down
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最好的  也是唯一的付款客户\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my best and only paying customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是巴里・霍普军士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Petty Officer Barry Hopper,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个海豹突击队员收到命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Navy SEAL who received orders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.01,0:06:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用便携核弹栽赃  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to plant evidence of suitcase nukes 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并暗杀了那个认定巴基斯坦没有核武器的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and to assassinate the nuclear inspector who had determined 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器核查员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that there were no such devices in Pakistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这段视频\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this is him
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记录了他执行命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}carrying out those orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:07:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而行动之后  便发生了核弹袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which were then followed by a nuclear first strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿什兰德上将  议长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}General Ashland, Mr. Speaker, 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都熟悉我的为人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you both know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我通常真的只顾自己  不管他人死活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I really don't care about anyone other than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果连我都感到义愤填膺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So if this got me pissed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们这些道德高尚  为人民服务的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what should it do to upstanding, civic-minded men
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做何感想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}such as yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你派了艘没有护卫的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're sending me a ship unescorted?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上有我们说好的供给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The supplies we promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告过你美国对此会有激进的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I warned you the U.S. response would be aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果中国不打算保护自己的船只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now if China isn't willing to defend its vessel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你有什么用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}why do I need you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前打算对自己国家...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you were willing to take on your country--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我冒着无法回国的危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't join with you at great cost
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你联手  为的可不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to any hopes I have of ever going home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换取你派来一艘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so that you could send me a ship
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连岸都靠不上的船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with little chance of ever reaching my shores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我们怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What would you have my country do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点用最好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be of use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言而有信  保卫你们自己的船只\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Back up your words and protect your own vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并跟美国宣战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And start a war with the U.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.12,0:07:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们愿意帮忙  艇长  但也要有限度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're willing to help, captain, but there are limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们自己都不打算救自己  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And why should we help you more than 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么还要帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you're willing to help yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果美国强迫其停船或者将其击沉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the U.S. stops this ship, maybe sinks it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那美国就成了国际舞台上的入侵者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it becomes the aggressor on the international stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.06,0:07:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果美国让船只通过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If it lets it through,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中国就成了人道主义者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}China becomes a great humanitarian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.64,0:08:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中国也是赢家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And it also wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算计得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You played this very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你什么也没给我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except that you've given me nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Untrue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便面临你国的威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Even in the face of threats from your nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我依然提供了食物供给\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I offer you food and aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哪个国家敢这么干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What other nation would even dare?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为你提供了在岛上生存的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Life on this island is what I offer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.67,0:08:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对外面的情况的处理  就是对我的回报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What happens out there is what you give me in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要与美国正面冲突\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You want a confrontation with the U.S.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少年来  美国都被看成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For how many years has the U.S. been seen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界超级霸权的守护者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as the guardian superpower of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理性的中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the rational center?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们政府不能再令人信服地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your administration can no longer claim that role
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扮演这个角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with any credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听清楚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会成为你们斗争的棋子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't be a proxy in your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着核武器库的棋子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A proxy with a nuclear arsenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的情况还不是最糟的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are worse things to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.18,0:08:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点  大使先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be careful, Mr. Ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在玩的游戏依然很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's still a very dangerous game you're playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与美国过招\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've swapped chess pieces with the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一天两天了  艇长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for many years now, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.54,0:08:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是美国\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not talking about the U.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各长官做好准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Officer on deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是查普林  我的车呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Chaplin. Where's my transport?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艇长  科罗拉多号还有20分钟入港\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, the Colorado Is still 20 minutes from port.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一到我们就派辆吉普过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll send a jeep for you as soon as they're close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's crazy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跑哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where you coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽艇出了点问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was, uh, some trouble with the launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我搞定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.88,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么能暖暖身子的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got anything back there to warm me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的任务改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's where our mission parameters changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到命令要栽赃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was ordered to plant evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以说明巴基斯坦对美国造成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that Pakistan posed an imminent nuclear threat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可预见的核威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我执行了命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I carried out that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想让我怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正午12点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}at 1200 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麦克奈尔堡的陆军分队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Army units out of Fort McNair
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将在麦克沃伊将军的指挥下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}under the command of General Macavoy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封锁全城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will shut the city down--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.30,0:10:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有桥梁和隧道都不许出入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all bridges, tunnels, no one in or out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时  在阿什兰德将军指挥下  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At the same time, the EADS, under General Ashland, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国会山上空将会建立禁飞区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will enforce a no-fly zone over the capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦这两项目标达成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And once those two objectives have been met,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里德将军手下的海军陆战队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A marine force recon contingent under General Reid
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将占领白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will take the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会把总统和副总统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And there they will place the president
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and the vice president under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此同时  议长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, Mr. Speaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会召开参众两院联席会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you will have already called a joint session of Congress,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.57,0:10:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阐明针对本届政府的弹劾案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and there you will outline the case against the administration
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为继任总统顺序表里的第三顺位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and announce that you, as third in the line of succession,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将就任总统一职\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are assuming the presidency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,副艇长怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How's the X.O. doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛失所爱的感觉一定无法想象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Must be horrible to lose someone you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.49,0:10:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到儿子死讯的时候还在海上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was at sea when I heard
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次作为艇长出航\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my first command.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一架直升机将我从亚得里亚海里接走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A helicopter plucked me out of the Adriatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在塞浦路斯找了一辆车\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took a transport from Cyprus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那里  我第一眼见到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the first thing I saw when I got there
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的两个儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}were my two boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也参加过战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我从未在任何人的眼里看到过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I've never seen fear in anyone's eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天我儿子们眼里的恐惧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}like I saw in the eyes of my sons that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'cause they knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妻子在一起最久的一段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My wife's illness was the longest continuous period of time 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.16,0:11:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她患病的那段时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that we ever spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而事实是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And the truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更像是娶了海军  而不是娶了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was more married to the navy than I ever was to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更像是我手下的好父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was a better father to the men under my command
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是我儿子们的好父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than I was to my own sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天很眷顾我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was given a blessing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢到根本没有意识到这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}too foolish to fully know what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.44,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有孩子  所以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't have any kids so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许我不知道我在说些什么  不过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe I don't know what I'm talking about, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你听到我在讨论某人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you heard me talk about someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你刚在讨论你自己那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the way that you just talked about yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会说我是个大八婆的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You would think that I was the biggest bitch walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时不用留在海上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't have to stay at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想当艇长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I wanted to make captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛是雪亮的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My eyes were open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚我是在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I knew exactly what I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just like I know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛是雪亮的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My eyes are open.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.98,0:12:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后一辆汽艇准备离港了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The last launch is ready to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉普车在待命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jeep's waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's our ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.30,0:12:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说有事要和我商量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said there was something you needed to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个漂亮女人  索菲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a beautiful woman, Sophie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在巴黎顶尖的学校接受的教育\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Been educated in the finest Parisian schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯于高品质的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're accustomed to the finer things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却把自己放逐到这座岛上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}yet you maroon yourself on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个鸟不拉屎的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作就在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is where my work is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你选择了在这里工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is where you choose your work to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在逃避生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're running away from life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想知道你是在逃避什么样的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't propose to know what pain it is you are running from,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你人在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你又在浪费你的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And now you are wasting yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痴望着已婚的海军军官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}mooning over this married naval officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道自己在说些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我了解你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.14,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我关心你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I care for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远超你所想象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}very deeply, more than you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我知道你关心这座岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I know you care for this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.58,0:13:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心着这座岛会变成什么样子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you worry about what will become of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信  最伟大的礼物  便是真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I believe the greatest gift is the gift of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-朱利安  -停  别说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Julian. - stop, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我另外雇了一个人做土壤测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had someone else run the soil test.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛富含稀土元素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This island is worth a fortune in rare earth elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我撒了谎  索菲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You lied to me, Sophie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱利安  如果你开采这些矿物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Julian, if you exploit those minerals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛上你所珍爱的一切都会被破坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}everything you love about this island will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么会认为我会破坏这座岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What makes you think I would destroy this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:13:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况会改变的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, the situation will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国佬会离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The Americans will leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:13:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会恢复正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and things will return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And when they do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么还要住在北约观察站里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}why live in the NATO housing
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是住在海边别墅里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when you can live in a villa on the coast?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以提供给你舒适  安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can provide for you comfort, security,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱利安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Julian.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好像刚吃了虫子一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You look as though you just ate a beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.64,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  我不是在向你求爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't worry. I'm not talking about love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you don't love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有弱点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Every man has a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我的弱点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能接受你不爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I accept you where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提意的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thus, what I propose
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种合作关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is a partnership...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.78,0:14:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于相互的感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}based on mutual affection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.00,0:14:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以一起照料这座岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can take care of this island together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以作为我的良知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can be my conscience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我可以满足你的任何心愿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I will reward my conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为对你的报答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with whatever her heart desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着时间推移  或许你会发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In time, you may find
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我也有了相同的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that you feel for me the same way I feel for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好胃口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bon appetit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Merci.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再有任何抱怨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No more public rumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再有条条框框\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No more breaking the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们解决这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We do this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出我们需要的人  等到时机成熟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Find the men we need, and then when the moment's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们接管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何不直接把他干掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why don't we just take him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一了百了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  不行 不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What? No. No, no, no. Hell, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能那么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are not doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我们的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is not what this is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他活着只能让事情变得更复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, keeping him alive only makes things more complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都想想本・拉登\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You all think about Bin Laden.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣动两下扳机  然后把尸体扔进印度洋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Double tap, dumped in the Indian Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就从此人间蒸发了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}he's out of sight, out of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华莱士  我们的艇长不是恐怖分子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wallace, our captain is not a terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, what the hell is he?
