Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.31,0:34:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饥渴慕义的人有福了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Blessed are they which do hunger and thirst after righteousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.04,0:34:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们必得饱足\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for they shall be filled with the spirit of god."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.93,0:34:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为义受逼迫的人有福了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"And blessed are those that are persecuted for righteousness' sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.18,0:34:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为天国是他们的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for theirs is the kingdom of heaven."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.89,0:34:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得真好  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's beautiful, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.56,0:34:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来  它说的是关于选择的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To me, it's about choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.69,0:34:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择去做正确的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Choosing to do the right thing
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.59,0:34:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使势单力孤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even though you are alone in that choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.75,0:34:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不让未知之恐惧扰乱思绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and not letting fear of the unknown cloud your thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.53,0:34:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕一旦前路渺茫  无法看清\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fear that, when the path becomes too hard to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.57,0:34:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会逃避回已知世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we run back to what we know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.69,0:34:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使已知世界已经彻底崩坏  无法修复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}even if what we know is broken beyond all repair.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.01,0:35:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们派你来杀我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did they send you here to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.94,0:35:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.60,0:35:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们现在正面临这样的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.06,0:35:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择的时刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Time to choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.85,0:35:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当中情局第一次接触我时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When the CIA first approached me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.66,0:35:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚大学毕业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was finishing up college...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.12,0:35:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有巨额学生贷款需要偿还\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Looking at a mountain of student loans.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.32,0:36:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后我在海军入伍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was already going into the navy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.45,0:36:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他们替我解决了一部分债务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}'cause they'd picked up some of the tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.60,0:36:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中情局又给了我一笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Langley was offering me a second paycheck
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.29,0:36:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我去处理一件可能永远不会发生的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for something they said would never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.68,0:36:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核潜艇艇长叛变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A nuclear sea captain going rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.83,0:36:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过要当间谍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never wanted to be a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.81,0:36:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想做好本职工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I just wanted to do my job well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.23,0:36:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这一切开始的那天起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From the day this started,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.14,0:36:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都无所适从\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't know what I was supposed to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.72,0:36:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道该站在哪一边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who I was supposed to stand by...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.30,0:36:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该相信谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who I believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.96,0:36:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我已经做出决定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've made that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.51,0:36:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很多敌人  科泰兹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have enemies, Cortez.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.50,0:36:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.03,0:36:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不是你的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I am not one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.21,0:37:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在已经开诚布公了  下一步呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now that we looked up each other's skirts, what do we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.17,0:37:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把对方活活打死吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}beat each other to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.65,0:37:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.71,0:37:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马库斯不能死  我要了解全部信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Marcus isn't dying. I need to know everything--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.39,0:37:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What the plan is,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.91,0:37:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艇员们有什么想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what the crew is thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.93,0:37:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.20,0:37:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到底层的秘密世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome to the deep end of the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.10,0:37:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上给我传送过去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.91,0:38:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市长先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Mayor,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.19,0:38:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何贵干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.41,0:38:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来送礼的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a gift--
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.63,0:38:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国波旁酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}American bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.93,0:38:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小批量珍藏款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Small batch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.80,0:38:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.09,0:38:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不好奇我是从哪搞到这东西的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you not at least curious as to how I acquire such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.74,0:38:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那根本想都不用想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That doesn't require very much imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.92,0:38:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, perhaps not.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.52,0:38:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样  我在这座岛上没有摆不平的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Either way, I am the man who gets things done on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.75,0:38:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为马库斯・查普林\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am confident that Marcus Chaplin
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.70,0:38:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是圣玛丽娜岛的主人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is the man in charge of Sainte Marina.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.26,0:38:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那或许是你的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you might think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.73,0:38:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许认为自己是因为政治原因而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You might think that you are here for political reasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.35,0:38:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you are mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.80,0:38:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是冲着我和我的东西而来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're here for me and what I have to offer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.70,0:38:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  这个岛的价值远超你的想象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, there's more to this island than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.32,0:38:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.38,0:38:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能给你无数个合适的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can give you a billion reasons why.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.29,0:38:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我一个就行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just give me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.46,0:38:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀土元素\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rare earth elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.30,0:38:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的石油\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The oil of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.47,0:38:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着这个样本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Take this sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.04,0:38:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去检测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.08,0:39:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你会非常高兴的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sure you will be very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.53,0:39:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.60,0:39:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.36,0:39:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.01,0:40:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, I'm okay. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.40,0:40:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.31,0:40:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我先说一句吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I... say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.13,0:40:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.13,0:40:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们美国人经常取笑我们法国人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You Americans make fun of the French.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.66,0:40:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们总在闹罢工  错过了摇滚乐的流行期\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're always on strike, we missed rock 'n' roll,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.61,0:40:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰瑞・路易斯[美国艺人]\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jerry Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.68,0:40:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们法国人...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, you know, we're not, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.33,0:40:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怕痛苦难受的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not scared about difficult feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.85,0:40:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要我在乎的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't need the people I care about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.27,0:40:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时刻都开开心心  明明白白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be happy all the time or clear
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都清清楚楚地知道想要什么  或不想要什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or know what they want or don't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.99,0:40:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以是一团乱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It can be a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.13,0:40:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们喜欢乱乱的状态\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We like messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.25,0:40:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你喜欢一团乱  那就找对人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if you like messy, I'm your guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.33,0:40:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以尽情取笑  但我不是在说笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're making fun of it, but I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.94,0:40:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.39,0:40:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法忍受继续看到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't stand seeing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.72,0:40:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此合不来  都没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't match. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.53,0:40:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索菲  走不走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sophie, are you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.17,0:41:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道伊迪丝・琵雅芙的一句法语箴言吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know this French saying from Edith Piaf,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.78,0:41:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无怨无悔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Je ne regrette rein"?
